# Copy to .env (gitignored) only if needed - not required for normal LAN dev.
#
# The API base URL and Firebase emulator host are auto-detected from the
# Metro dev server's own LAN address (see src/lib/dev-host.ts). Set this to
# override that detection - e.g. when using `expo start --tunnel`, or an
# iOS Simulator/Android emulator where "localhost" should be used instead.
# EXPO_PUBLIC_DEV_HOST=192.168.1.23
